    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>chopped pepper</strong> and <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened but not browned</p>",
