    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[510ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> chipotle stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black</strong> <strong>beans</strong></p>",
