    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
