      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash cubes are cooked through, gently mash <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>black beans</strong> roughly with a fork</p><p>Squeeze in the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> black bean & squash chilli</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime[s] </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
